# ELECTRA TPS Management Frontend — Implementation Plan

## Overview

Build the complete frontend for ELECTRA — a TPS (Polling Station) Management Dashboard for PAN (Partai Amanat Nasional) in Sukoharjo, Indonesia. The frontend is a React 19 + TypeScript + Vite application with Tailwind CSS v4, connecting to a Laravel Sanctum backend API already running at `http://localhost:8000`.

**Current state**: Frontend is nearly empty — only `main.tsx` (with a router import that doesn't exist yet) and a blank `index.css`. All code needs to be built from scratch.

## Backend API Summary (Already Built)

| Endpoint | Method | Description |
|---|---|---|
| `POST /api/auth/login` | POST | Login (returns token) |
| `POST /api/auth/logout` | POST | Logout |
| `GET /api/auth/profile` | GET | Current user profile |
| `GET /api/dashboard` | GET | Dashboard stats (total_tps, active_tps, covered_tps, total_officers, assignment_completion_rate, by_district[]) |
| `GET /api/polling-stations` | GET | Paginated list (filters: district_id, village_id, status, search, per_page) |
| `POST /api/polling-stations` | POST | Create station |
| `GET /api/polling-stations/{id}` | GET | Show with assignments/vote_result |
| `PUT /api/polling-stations/{id}` | PUT | Update station |
| `DELETE /api/polling-stations/{id}` | DELETE | Soft delete |
| `POST /api/polling-stations/import` | POST | Import XLS file |
| `GET /api/polling-stations/map-data` | GET | GeoJSON map data |
| `GET /api/polling-stations/export` | GET | Excel export |
| `GET /api/districts` | GET | List districts |
| `GET /api/villages` | GET | List villages |
| `GET /api/officers` | GET | Paginated (filters: district_id, role, status, search) |
| `POST /api/officers` | POST | Create |
| `PUT /api/officers/{id}` | PUT | Update |
| `DELETE /api/officers/{id}` | DELETE | Delete |
| `GET /api/assignments` | GET | Paginated (filters: polling_station_id, officer_id, confirmation_status) |
| `POST /api/assignments` | POST | Create |
| `PATCH /api/assignments/{id}/confirm` | PATCH | Confirm assignment |
| `DELETE /api/assignments/{id}` | DELETE | Delete |
| `GET /api/vote-results` | GET | Paginated (filters: district_id, verified; `?aggregate=true` for per-district) |
| `POST /api/vote-results` | POST | Submit result |
| `PUT /api/vote-results/{id}` | PUT | Update result |

**API Response shape**: `{ success: boolean, message: string, data: T, meta?: { current_page, last_page, per_page, total } }`

**Backend Enums**:
- `PollingStationStatus`: `active` | `inactive` | `review`
- `OfficerRole`: `coordinator` | `kpps` | `witness` | `observer`
- `OfficerStatus`: `active` | `inactive`
- `ConfirmationStatus`: `confirmed` | `pending` | `absent`

---

