### Phase 2: Types & i18n & API Services

#### [NEW] `src/types/index.ts`
All TypeScript interfaces mapped exactly to backend API responses:
- `District` (id, code, name, geojson_key)
- `Village` (id, district_id, code, name)
- `PollingStation` (id, station_number, venue_name, address, district, village, status, lat, lng, notes, officer_count, assignments, vote_result)
- `Officer` (id, name, phone, email, role, district, status, assignments_count)
- `Assignment` (id, polling_station, officer, role, confirmation_status, notes, assigned_at, confirmed_at)
- `VoteResult` (id, polling_station, party_votes, total_votes, dpt, voters_present, submitter, submitted_at, verified)
- `DashboardStats` (total_tps, active_tps, covered_tps, total_officers, assignment_completion_rate, by_district)
- `ApiResponse<T>`, `PaginatedResponse<T>`
- Enums: `PollingStationStatus`, `OfficerRole`, `OfficerStatus`, `ConfirmationStatus`

#### [NEW] `src/types/schemas.ts`
Zod validation schemas for all forms:
- `pollingStationSchema`, `officerSchema`, `assignmentSchema`, `voteResultSchema`

#### [NEW] `src/i18n/index.ts`
i18next configuration with EN/ID detection, localStorage persistence

#### [NEW] `src/i18n/locales/en.json`
Complete English translations (~200 keys): nav, common, dashboard, polling stations, officers, assignments, vote results, forms, validation messages

#### [NEW] `src/i18n/locales/id.json`
Complete Indonesian translations matching en.json

#### [NEW] `src/services/api.ts`
Axios instance with:
- baseURL from `VITE_API_BASE_URL`
- Request interceptor: inject Bearer token from cookie/localStorage
- Response interceptor: 401 → redirect to login, extract error messages

#### [NEW] `src/services/polling-station.service.ts`
Typed functions: `getPollingStations(filters)`, `getPollingStation(id)`, `createPollingStation(data)`, `updatePollingStation(id, data)`, `deletePollingStation(id)`, `importPollingStations(file)`, `getMapData(filters)`, `exportPollingStations(filters)`

#### [NEW] `src/services/officer.service.ts`
`getOfficers(filters)`, `getOfficer(id)`, `createOfficer(data)`, `updateOfficer(id, data)`, `deleteOfficer(id)`

#### [NEW] `src/services/assignment.service.ts`
`getAssignments(filters)`, `createAssignment(data)`, `updateAssignment(id, data)`, `deleteAssignment(id)`, `confirmAssignment(id)`

#### [NEW] `src/services/vote-result.service.ts`
`getVoteResults(filters)`, `getVoteResultAggregation()`, `createVoteResult(data)`, `updateVoteResult(id, data)`

#### [NEW] `src/services/dashboard.service.ts`
`getDashboardStats()`

#### [NEW] `src/services/region.service.ts`
`getDistricts()`, `getVillages(districtId?)`

#### [NEW] `src/lib/query-keys.ts`
