### Phase 3: Custom UI Component Library (`src/components/ui/`)

All 20+ components, custom-built from scratch with Tailwind CSS. Every component:
- Fully typed with TypeScript (no `any`)
- Supports dark mode via CSS variables
- ARIA accessible
- Composable and reusable

| File | Component | Key Features |
|---|---|---|
| `button.tsx` | Button | 5 variants, 3 sizes, loading spinner, icon support |
| `input.tsx` | Input | Label, error state, icon, hint, dark mode |
| `select.tsx` | Select | Custom dropdown, searchable, keyboard nav |
| `modal.tsx` | Modal, ConfirmModal | Portal, backdrop blur, focus trap, ESC close, scale animation |
| `badge.tsx` | Badge | 6 variants, dot indicator, sm/md sizes |
| `card.tsx` | Card, CardHeader, CardBody, CardFooter | Hover lift, click, padding variants |
| `table.tsx` | Table | Striped rows, skeleton loading, sort arrows, sticky header |
| `dropdown.tsx` | Dropdown | Action menu, slide animation, danger items, dividers |
| `toast.tsx` | ToastProvider, useToast | Bottom-right stack, auto-dismiss, progress bar |
| `spinner.tsx` | Spinner | CSS-only rotating ring, 3 sizes/colors |
| `skeleton.tsx` | Skeleton, SkeletonText, SkeletonCard, SkeletonTable | Shimmer animation |
| `tabs.tsx` | Tabs | Line/pill variants, slide underline animation |
| `alert.tsx` | Alert | Left border accent, matching lucide icons |
| `progress.tsx` | Progress | Animated fill, color variants, label + percent |
| `avatar.tsx` | Avatar | Initials fallback (auto-color by name), online dot |
| `switch.tsx` | Switch | Slide toggle animation, label, error |
| `checkbox.tsx` | Checkbox | Styled matching design, label, error |
| `radio.tsx` | Radio | Styled matching design, RadioGroup |
| `textarea.tsx` | Textarea | Label, error, hint, auto-resize option |
| `index.ts` | Barrel export | Re-exports all components |

